    "title": "Shhh. I'll take care of everything, don't you fret.",
    "description": "While equipped, regenerates SMG reserve ammo at 1.5 per second.\n\nReload throws the weapon forwards; it ricochets off targets and scenery, keeps firing in all directions, then detonates after a short fuse (roughly 0.1 to 3.6s). When SMG reserve ammo drops below 57, the fuse shortens.\n\nDetonation damage scales with shot damage and unused ammo (fire). The thrown gun's bullets deal physical grenade-type damage and benefit from gun and amp damage bonuses."
